WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.800
Your pricing page has six options. That's why nobody picks one.

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:12.300
Every option is a comparison the buyer has to run. Past a few, deciding costs more than choosing is worth.

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:16.330
And when deciding gets expensive, not choosing feels safe.

00:00:16.330 --> 00:00:21.830
Count the decisions on your homepage. Every button, every plan, every maybe.

00:00:21.830 --> 00:00:26.270
Cut until one path is obvious. Confidence follows clarity.

00:00:26.270 --> 00:00:30.930
A confused buyer doesn't choose wrong. They just don't choose.

00:00:30.933 --> 00:00:33.418
Perception and attention intelligence.

00:00:33.418 --> 00:00:41.403
If you want to see where buyers stall on your page, we break it down every week. Free, at arstrategists.com.
